00:21:49.007 --> 00:21:50.008 line:95%,end
But it's not right.

00:21:50.075 --> 00:21:52.811 line:95%,end
MELLISA: <i>We had 30 minutes</i>
<i>to get our kids ready.</i>

00:21:52.878 --> 00:21:54.012 line:95%,end
<i>They had to be stretched.</i>

00:21:54.079 --> 00:21:55.847 line:95%,end
<i>We had to put French twists in their hair,</i>

00:21:55.914 --> 00:21:57.616 line:95%,end
<i>fake eyelashes, all their makeup.</i>

00:21:57.683 --> 00:21:58.750 line:95%,end
It was crazy.

00:22:00.619 --> 00:22:03.355 line:95%,end
Maddie, you have one number
to dance and that's it.

00:22:03.922 --> 00:22:04.923 line:95%,end
You're going to deal with it.

00:22:04.990 --> 00:22:06.091 line:95%,end
Be a grownup.

00:22:07.592 --> 00:22:08.860 line:95%,end
I'm sick of this attitude.

00:22:08.927 --> 00:22:11.196 line:5%,start
I can't deal with Maddie's attitude.

00:22:11.263 --> 00:22:13.932 line:5%,start
She's eight years old
and sometimes she thinks she's 16.

00:22:14.633 --> 00:22:17.302 line:95%,end
