-Not those.

00:22:17.369 --> 00:22:20.005 line:95%,end
No. Maddie, calm down, please.

00:22:20.072 --> 00:22:21.273 line:5%,start
I'm a perfectionist.

00:22:21.340 --> 00:22:24.242 line:95%,end
<i>I don't like to be rushed</i>
<i>when I'm doing my makeup and hair.</i>

00:22:25.077 --> 00:22:26.845 line:95%,end
MELISSA: Guess what?
Do you want to go home?

00:22:27.245 --> 00:22:29.081 line:95%,end
