00:22:41.626 --> 00:22:44.062 line:95%,end
<i>Melissa is always on time,</i>
<i>always prepared,</i>

00:22:44.129 --> 00:22:45.330 line:95%,end
<i>always where she needs to be.</i>

00:22:45.397 --> 00:22:48.867 line:5%,start
And when that doesn't happen
exactly as she planned,

00:22:48.934 --> 00:22:50.369 line:5%,start
then she gets worked up.

00:22:50.435 --> 00:22:52.237 line:95%,end
And that, in turn, works up her daughters.

00:22:52.304 --> 00:22:53.905 line:95%,end
Girls--sh, stop.

00:22:53.972 --> 00:22:57.809 line:95%,end
<i>There are 1,500 numbers.</i>

00:22:57.876 --> 00:22:58.844 line:95%,end
<i>Okay?</i>

00:22:58.910 --> 00:23:00.979 line:95%,end
You're the first thing you're going
to see from Abby Lee Miller.

00:23:01.046 --> 00:23:02.314 line:95%,end
