00:23:02.381 --> 00:23:04.116 line:95%,end
Be respectful backstage.

00:23:04.182 --> 00:23:05.817 line:95%,end
When you come off the stage,

00:23:05.884 --> 00:23:08.086 line:95%,end
I don't care if it was good,
bad or otherwise.

00:23:08.153 --> 00:23:09.955 line:95%,end
You act like it was the best time
you ever danced.

00:23:10.021 --> 00:23:11.123 line:95%,end
