00:23:11.189 --> 00:23:12.991 line:95%,end
This is what we have been
working for all season.

00:23:13.058 --> 00:23:15.327 line:95%,end
Today is what matters, right now
in 10 minutes.

00:23:15.394 --> 00:23:16.361 line:95%,end
