00:23:18.430 --> 00:23:21.433 line:95%,end
(upbeat music playing)

00:23:23.802 --> 00:23:26.805 line:95%,end
(dramatic music playing)

00:23:29.741 --> 00:23:32.177 line:5%,start
MELISSA: Every single competition
