00:38:52.697 --> 00:38:54.465 line:95%,end
There's a Satan theme.

00:38:54.532 --> 00:38:56.834 line:95%,end
It's like, there's a little undertone,
a nuance that

00:38:56.901 --> 00:38:58.836 line:95%,end
