00:39:14.485 --> 00:39:15.753 line:95%,end
for what she does well.

00:39:15.820 --> 00:39:17.054 line:95%,end
She doesn't have good feet.

00:39:17.121 --> 00:39:18.456 line:95%,end
She doesn't have great turnout.

00:39:18.522 --> 00:39:20.991 line:95%,end
She doesn't straighten her knees.
She's sway back.

00:39:21.058 --> 00:39:23.361 line:95%,end
